<terms>
<item>
<title><code>do_close</code></title>
  <p>Whether to close the channel on the final unref of
           the GIOChannel data structure. The default value of
           this is <code>true</code> for channels created by g_io_channel_new_file (),
           and <code>false</code> for all other channels.</p>
